comments: Replay review of the foul called on Schroder (TOR) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Schroder (TOR) delivers contact to Young (ATL) that dislodges Young from his legally obtained defensive position at the end of his drive.
Dick (TOR) moves along Young's (ATL) path and absorbs the marginal contact that occurs during his drive.
Dick (TOR) moves laterally into Young's (ATL) path and initiates body contact that affects Young's SQBR during the drive.
Johnson (ATL) moves into Barnes' (TOR) path and initiates body contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brown (TOR) places his hand to Johnson's (ATL) side and marginal body contact occurs during his shot attempt at the basket.
Barnes (TOR) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Capela's (ATL) arm after the release.
Trent Jr. (TOR) contests the layup attempt and marginal contact occurs with Bey's (ATL) hand after the release.
Bogdanovic (ATL) reaches in and initiates contact with Brown's (TOR) wrist, which causes him to lose control of the ball.
Nwora (TOR) initiates contact with Young's (ATL) front, affecting his SQBR during the drive.
Trent Jr. (TOR) establishes himself in Johnson's (ATL) path and absorbs the contact.
Young (ATL) hedges the pick and absorbs the marginal body contact, moving alongside Barnes' (TOR) path during his drive.
Nwora (TOR) moves along Young's (ATL) path and marginal contact occurs to Young's hip contesting his driving shot attempt.
Capela (ATL) lifts his arm into a vertical position, at the end of Barnes' (TOR) drive, and lowers it, initiating contact with Barnes' wrist which affects his shot attempt.
Johnson (ATL) jumps alongside Dick (TOR) and marginal body contact occurs during Dick's shot attempt at the basket.
Nwora (TOR) continues to move into and makes contact with Young's (ATL) lower body, affecting his SQBR during his drive in transition.
Trent Jr (TOR) jumps alongside Young's (ATL) path and lightly brushes his arm defending his driving shot attempt.
Bey (ATL) makes contact with the ball after it exits the imaginary cylinder above the rim.
Bogdanovic (ATL) brings his arm toward Nwora's (TOR) path and immediately removes it as marginal contact occurs as Nwora gathers the ball at the end of his drive.
